'''fussballdaten.de''' is a [[German language]] [[website]] which predominantly collects comprehensive statistics on the [[German football league system|top five tiers]] of [[Football in Germany|German football]].

The website offers statistics on every [[Fußball-Bundesliga|Bundesliga]], [[2. Fußball-Bundesliga|2. Bundesliga]] and [[3. Fußball-Liga|3. Liga]] match and team squad since the leagues' foundation in 1963, 1974 and 2008, respectively.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stroeer-interactive.de/advertiser/portfolio/sites/fussballdaten-de|title=fussballdaten.de|work=[[Ströer]]|accessdate=4 August 2010|language=German}}</ref>

